snippet.title: Sel Mounta: Siege The Demon Castle! Game Trailer
snippet.description:
It's ready at last! The trailer for our third game, the sequel to Sel Quinta, The Six City Quest! It's a bit of an unusual format for a trailer, maybe not as flashy as some but it should still give a good idea of what the game is about! The game itself can be found here and is now released!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2432060/Sel_MountaSiege_the_Demon_Castle/

However, I do have a link for the game it continues on from-and Sel Quinta is fully free to play too! No catch, just outright free! So if you want to go take a look and get up to date on the story, check it out below!
Sel Quinta
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1891680/Sel_Quinta__The_Six_City_Quest/

The BWI Games discord! Want to talk about the FTD tourneys, stuff we've been playing or making, or want news/previews on what I'm working on? Those you'll find here: https://discord.gg/4x2drgya

And our slightly older game IORC

IORC
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1636380/IORC__Impact_Orbital_Rescue_Crew/
